metadata.name: ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ Corporate Psychosis ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ #1/5
metadata.description: The corporate world's madness is embodied in him, a man of many faces in a red suit of psychosis. His eyes dart between screens, his mind constantly racing. He represents the rat race, consumed by greed and ambition. The world whirls around him, a dizzying blur of numbers and contracts. He is the king of his little empire, but at what cost? The weight of his decisions and actions bears down upon him, but he keeps moving forward, driven by the relentless pursuit of success. He is invincible in his mind, but in reality, he is just another cog in the machine.
